        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Energy Savings and Building Efficiency Act of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill revises provisions related to building energy codes, including by directing the Department of Energy to provide technical assistance to states, Indian tribes, and local governments to implement technically feasible and cost-effective building energy codes.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
